modules.description: This module extends the `PrintBox` system with rich plotting capabilities, enabling the creation of scatterplots, line graphs, decision boundaries, and custom mapped plots using `PrintBox.t` elements. It supports structured graph configurations with axis labels, size, precision, and optional axes rendering, while allowing precise control over visual elements through functions that map coordinates to boxes. Concrete use cases include visualizing mathematical functions, plotting data points with associated labels or markers, and rendering decision boundaries for classification problems.
